# Workflow Templates

## New Deployment
1. Copy script to server.
2. Test connectivity.
3. Run dry-run.
4. Verify results.
5. Execute with caution.
6. Verify results.

## Standard Maintenance
1. Check connectivity.
2. Review retention policy.
3. Execute dry-run.
4. Analyze output logs.
5. Execute if safe.
6. Verify results.

## Troubleshooting Workflow
1. Test basic connectivity.
2. Verify SSH key permissions.
3. Check PowerShell execution policy.
4. Review error logs.
5. Test with minimal parameters.
6. Verify results.